  name: "Oppo HA-2", avg_score: 9, category: "Amplifier", info: "High-resolution USB DAC for Apple/Android/PC/Mac ESS Sabre32 Reference ES9018-K2M DAC chip.Two gain settings for optimal headphone matching.Mobile power bank for charging your phone" , image_url: "http://cdn.head-fi.org/9/97/97a963b7_IMG_1735_OPPO_HA-2_with_iPad_Mini_and_OPPO_PM-1_05_x960.jpeg"
